body.description: This Travelon's Waterproof Smart Pouch protects your mobile phone or any other small electronic device while on an adventure or traveling near water. This waterproof phone pouch fits virtually all mobile phones and features a soft outer surface that allows you to control your personal electronic devices without taking them out of the pouch. For more than 35 years Travelon has been making travel easier and safer with products that provide protection, peace-of-mind, safety, security, and organization.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: We create more stress-free journeys Simply put, there is no other product made like a TRAVELON product. Product quality, selection, and innovation are key attributes that have made TRAVELON a leading travel accessory and travel lifestyle brand. itFloats Waterproof Phone Pouch A vacation essential, and a must-have for water activities Outdoor activities and travel often involve water. Try out our itFloats Waterproof Phone Pouch. Features include: Large mobile phone capacity, including: iPhone 14 Pro Max, Galaxy S22 Ultra, OnePlus 10 Pro and the Pixel 6 Pro IPX8 Certified Waterproof Phone Case is waterproof up to 30M/100ft Floatation pillow ensures your phone won't sink and is easy to spot in open water Simple snap-and-lock access keeps out snow, water, sand, and dirt Crystal-clear TPU windows make it easy to take pictures and videos or check texts and emails Touch screen access for talk and text

Travelon itFloats Waterproof Phone Pouch Protect Your Phone Outdoor activities and travel often involve water. Keep your phone safe and dry with our Waterproof Phone Pouch! This phone pouch is submersible to 100ft (30M) for 30 minutes. Touch screen is accessible through pouch allowing talk, text and photography on your trip. Have fun This case can protect your phone from water, dirt, dust or sand! Have fun on your trip and keep a peace of mind knowing your phone is safe - and more importantly - dry. Be Bold Our itFloats Waterproof Phone Pouch comes in bold colors.
